Joseph Singleton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Singleton 0 Joseph Edward Victor Fairfield Daveran Singleton (1 March 1879 – 24 October 1946) was an Australian actor of the silent era. He appeared in 74 films between 1913 and 1925. He was born in Melbourne.
